@av8ramit I see that the precompiled GPU binary (libtensorflow_framework.so) contains this symbol:

_ZN10tensorflow12OpDefBuilder4AttrEN4absl11string_viewE

whereas the CPU one contains:

_ZN10tensorflow12OpDefBuilder4AttrESs

Should this be expected? And even so, why does this inconsistency exist?
